  Assistance for the snowman was provided by the snowman code from Dr. Teather
  Assistance for the lighting was supported by the Teapot code from Dr. Teather
  Assistance for the light colors was provided by:
       		https://www.opengl.org/discussion_boards/showthread.php/132502-Color-tables
  Assistance for the calculation of the cross product was given by:
       		http://www.mathsisfun.com/algebra/vectors-cross-product.html
  Assistance for the multi-window aspect was provided by:
       		http://deslab.mit.edu/DesignLab/courses/13.016/graphics/multi.html
  Assistance for the fault and the circle algorithm was provided by:
       		http://www.lighthouse3d.com/opengl/terrain/index.php3?circles

